        {
            "heading": "Azure Services Cheat Sheet",
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": "### Base Services\n| Azure Service | Purpose | Like AWS |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| Virtual Machines | Host full servers (IaaS) | EC2 |\n| Web Apps | Managed website hosting (PaaS) | Elastic Beanstalk |\n| SQL Database | Managed SQL Server | RDS |\n| Storage Blobs | Unstructured object storage | S3 |\n| Key Vault | Secure secret/cert management | KMS / Secrets Manager |\n| Virtual Network | Private network isolation | VPC |\n| Functions | Serverless compute | Lambda |\n| Logic Apps | Workflow automation | Step Functions |"
        },
        {
            "heading": "Azure Security Toolset",
            "type": "list",
            "content": [
                "[ROADtools](https://github.com/dirkjanm/ROADtools) - Azure AD exploration and visualization",
                "[AzureHound](https://github.com/BloodHoundAD/AzureHound) - BloodHound for Azure infrastructure",
                "[AADInternals](https://github.com/Gerenios/AADInternals) - Powerful Azure AD management tool",
                "[MicroBurst](https://github.com/NetSPI/MicroBurst) - Large suite of Azure security tools",
                "[PowerZure](https://github.com/hausec/PowerZure) - Post-exploitation script for Azure"
            ]
        },
